Emal to Invest $3.8 Bln in Second Expansion Phase, Alrroya Says

-- B y   T a m a r a   W a l i d
-- 
2011-12-13T05:19:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/emal-to-invest-3-8-bln-in-second-expansion-phase-alrroya-says.html
Emirates Aluminium Co., based in  Abu
Dhabi , plans to invest $3.8 billion in an expansion program as
it aims to become the largest smelter in the world,  Alrroya
reported , citing Chief Executive Officer Saeed Al Mazrooei.  A first expansion phase was completed several months ago.
Work has begun on the second, for which German companies have
been awarded contracts worth $184 million, Al Mazrooei said.
